%^RESET%^%^BOLD%^%^GREEN%^Prestige Class
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Versatile Arcanist:

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Requirements:
%^RESET%^ Level 40 Character
%^RESET%^ Level 20 Sorcerer
%^RESET%^ 20 Points Spent in the Spellcraft Skill
%^RESET%^ 20 Base Charisma (before equipment modifiers)

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Class Feats:%^RESET%^
 %^RESET%^L1: greater spell knowledge
 %^RESET%^L4: master of elements
 %^RESET%^L7: master of versatility

Versatile arcanists have a flexible understanding of the weave that onlyrare sorcerers ever truly obtain. Such mastery of arcana extends not onlyto the sorcerer's instinctive understanding of magic and magical items,but also grants a command of spells that most normal sorcerers nevermanage to learn.

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^See also: %^RESET%^feats, skills, spells, cast, prepare, master